aisphalt cement or thos bitumen main upasthit ghatak jo carbon dicelphide main viley
aisphalt cement: galit yaa agalit aisphalt jise bitumini patari ke nirmaan main sidhe prayog ke liye vishisht gunata kaa banaaya jaataa he.
aisphalt: sadak nirmaan main prayukt bitumen tathaa khanijon kaa mishran.
aisphaltite: ucch galnaank vaale thos hydrocarbon. udaahranarth gilsonite tathaa glanspich jinka galnaank
aisphalti avshisht: aisphalt se bana yaa aisphalt ke samaan bana hua. aksar yah aisphalt yukt aprishkrut telon se bane snehak telon ke liye prayukt hota he.
aisphalti tel: snehan kii drushti se yen naphthenic tel ke sadrishy padaarth hote hai.
aisphalti petroleum: aisphalt kii paryaapt maatra yukt petroleum.

aisphalti sadak tel: aisphalt kaa gadha taral vilyan. kabhi kabhi petroleum ke baari aprishkrut aisphalt kaa prayog kiya jaataa he kintu adhiktar aprishkrut aisphalt petroleum ke adhik vashpashil ghatakon ke aswan se praapt tel prayag hota he.
